        {"id":"e6","difficulty":"medium","body_en":"Gauss-Jordan: find $A^{-1}$ for $A=\\begin{pmatrix}1&2\\\\3&7\\end{pmatrix}$.","body_he":"גאוס-ג'ורדן: $A=\\begin{pmatrix}1&2\\\\3&7\\end{pmatrix}$. $A^{-1}$?","solution_en":"$[A|I]\\to\\begin{pmatrix}1&2&|&1&0\\\\0&1&|&-3&1\\end{pmatrix}\\to\\begin{pmatrix}1&0&|&7&-2\\\\0&1&|&-3&1\\end{pmatrix}$. $A^{-1}=\\begin{pmatrix}7&-2\\\\-3&1\\end{pmatrix}$.","solution_he":"$A^{-1}=\\begin{pmatrix}7&-2\\\\-3&1\\end{pmatrix}$."},
        {"id":"e7","difficulty":"medium","body_en":"$\\det(A)=3$, $A$ is $3\\times3$. Find $\\det(A^{-1})$.","body_he":"$\\det(A)=3$. $\\det(A^{-1})$?","solution_en":"$\\det(A^{-1})=1/3$.","solution_he":"$1/3$."},
        {"id":"e8","difficulty":"medium","body_en":"$A=\\begin{pmatrix}1&1\\\\1&2\\end{pmatrix}$. Solve $Ax=\\begin{pmatrix}5\\\\9\\end{pmatrix}$.","body_he":"$Ax=\\begin{pmatrix}5\\\\9\\end{pmatrix}$. פתרון?","solution_en":"$\\det=1$. $A^{-1}=\\begin{pmatrix}2&-1\\\\-1&1\\end{pmatrix}$. $x=\\begin{pmatrix}10-9\\\\-5+9\\end{pmatrix}=\\begin{pmatrix}1\\\\4\\end{pmatrix}$.","solution_he":"$x=(1,4)^T$."},
        {"id":"e9","difficulty":"medium","body_en":"If $A^2=I$, what is $A^{-1}$?","body_he":"אם $A^2=I$, מהי $A^{-1}$?","solution_en":"$A\\cdot A=I\\Rightarrow A^{-1}=A$.","solution_he":"$A^{-1}=A$."},
        {"id":"e10","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"Find $A^{-1}$ for $A=\\begin{pmatrix}1&2&0\\\\0&1&3\\\\0&0&1\\end{pmatrix}$.","body_he":"$A=\\begin{pmatrix}1&2&0\\\\0&1&3\\\\0&0&1\\end{pmatrix}$. $A^{-1}$?","solution_en":"$[A|I]$, reduce: back-substitute. $A^{-1}=\\begin{pmatrix}1&-2&6\\\\0&1&-3\\\\0&0&1\\end{pmatrix}$.","solution_he":"$A^{-1}=\\begin{pmatrix}1&-2&6\\\\0&1&-3\\\\0&0&1\\end{pmatrix}$."},
        {"id":"e11","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"Prove: if $A$ is invertible, then $Ax=b$ has a unique solution.","body_he":"הוכח: אם $A$ הפיכה, $Ax=b$ מוסבר יחידאית.","solution_en":"$x=A^{-1}b$: this is a solution (verify $A(A^{-1}b)=Ib=b$). Unique: if $Ax=b$ and $Ay=b$, then $A(x-y)=0\\Rightarrow x-y=A^{-1}\\cdot0=0\\Rightarrow x=y$.","solution_he":"$x=A^{-1}b$ פתרון. יחידאי: $A(x-y)=0\\Rightarrow x=y$."},
        {"id":"e12","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"$A$ and $B$ are invertible $n\\times n$. Show $(AB)^{-1}=B^{-1}A^{-1}$.","body_he":"הוכח $(AB)^{-1}=B^{-1}A^{-1}$.","solution_en":"$(AB)(B^{-1}A^{-1})=A(BB^{-1})A^{-1}=AIA^{-1}=AA^{-1}=I$. ✓","solution_he":"$(AB)(B^{-1}A^{-1})=A(BB^{-1})A^{-1}=I$ ✓."},
        {"id":"e13","difficulty":"hard","body_en":"For what values of $k$ does $A=\\begin{pmatrix}k&1&0\\\\1&k&1\\\\0&1&k\\end{pmatrix}$ have no inverse?","body_he":"עבור אילו $k$ המטריצה $\\begin{pmatrix}k&1&0\\\\1&k&1\\\\0&1&k\\end{pmatrix}$ אינה הפיכה?","solution_en":"$\\det(A)=k(k^2-1)-1(k-0)=k^3-k-k=k^3-2k=k(k^2-2)=0$. $k=0$, $k=\\pm\\sqrt{2}$.","solution_he":"$k=0$, $k=\\pm\\sqrt{2}$."}
